data: {"type": "text-delta", "id": "279bc988-26ca-4169-806a-e2e8ca47d330", "delta": "To check if a systemd service is active on RHEL 9:\n\n*   **Script-friendly (yes/no):** `systemctl is-active <service_name>`\n    *   Returns `active` if running, `inactive` or `failed` otherwise.\n*   **Detailed status:** `systemctl status <service_name>`\n    *   Shows active state, recent logs, and process details.\n\nReplace `<service_name>` with the actual service (e.g., `httpd`, `sshd`)."}

data: {"type": "text-end", "id": "279bc988-26ca-4169-806a-e2e8ca47d330"}

