data: {"type": "text-delta", "id": "361bb52c-9149-4528-bb12-32ff88a9dc8a", "delta": "To check if a systemd service is active on RHEL 9:\n\n- **Quick check (exit code):**  \n  `systemctl is-active <service>`  \n  Returns `active`, `inactive`, or `failed`.\n\n- **Detailed status:**  \n  `systemctl status <service>`  \n  Shows active state, recent logs, and process info.\n\nExample:  \n`systemctl is-active httpd` → `active`  \n`systemctl status httpd` → full status output"}

